
o if several forwarders are specified the most valuable is selected

	- if both are operating then the time is measured and
	  after a few samples the best is picked for a specified amount
		of time.

	- If one forwarder do not response within e specified time
	  then the fallback if back to one of the other nameservers

	- If a nameserver is detected to be unoperational, then this
	  nameserver is server is marked as beeing unoperational and avoided.
		After a predefined time then nameserver is re-probed again.
